[center]Welcome to the Clan -[i] King Of Wild[/i][/center]
To join this clan, you need a combat level of 95 or more. Visit www.kingofwild.smfforfree4.com We are looking for a lot of people and we plan on growing this clan huge!
It`s simple to join; simply register + you don`t even need to confirm activation codes, signing up is instent!
The activities that were going to be doing:
- F2p/P2p Bounty Hunting - Monster killing (Kingbd, Kalphite, Barrows, God Dongeone ETC) - Somtimes we will do group quests but not too often
JOIN NOW!
www.kingofwild.smfforfree4.com
